{"lastModified":1773263767215,"uri":"c::7579706445::vessel::77947fe5-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nTamiro is our Lagoon 52F, a luxurious catamaran based in the Ionian available for fully crewed charters in the beautiful Greek waters.\n\nHaving its starting base from the islands of Lefkas or Corfu, she is equipped with 4 cabins and 4 WCs, offering an ideal layout for 4 couples or 2 families.\n\nTamiro allows you to delight in an eco-friendly cruising by not only reducing your carbon footprint but also providing a continuous and sustainable source of power, by featuring an advanced solar and lithium system.\n\nRelish your time aboard with the seamless connection and intuitive flow between the spacious, modern interior and the elegant outdoor areas, expertly designed for entertainment and socializing. Combined with the catamaran's exceptional maneuverability, sailing performance and stability and you have a floating dream villa that offers uninterrupted sea views of Greece's most stunning locations.","blueprint":{"name":"TAMIRO","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::77947fe5-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::64e4a680-d5c7-11f0-a25b-add3ef8e3ccc/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::77947fe5-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::64b8db90-d5c7-11f0-8748-f91ed5e9249d/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::77947fe5-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::64f1ecf0-d5c7-11f0-8748-f91ed5e9249d/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::77947fe5-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::64b53210-d5c7-11f0-a25b-add3ef8e3ccc/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::77947fe5-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::64eae810-d5c7-11f0-a25b-add3ef8e3ccc/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::77947fe5-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::64b3ab70-d5c7-11f0-a25b-add3ef8e3ccc/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::77947fe5-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::6